task.summary: Added StolenVehicle class and json. Changed Dates to longs
Updated some entity relations to work with id's instead of hard references to compensate for storage across multiple databases.

Removed implementation of domain classes, replaced them with interfaces. This is required in order to prevent all classes from being converted to database entities in every application that uses them.
